{"id": "1249249419258363955", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T06:31:11.483000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1249249419069751376", "filename": "Screenshot_20240609_073017__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 157608, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1180850818509971466/1249249419069751376/Screenshot_20240609_073017__Morimens.jpg?ex=6a37852f&is=6a3633af&hm=328bd9521aebf1aba17b17c99033d44b9fbdad7510aa5d6ec8410925464573c5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1249249663152820245", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "測完後我改成這樣了\n@0.0._.0_0.", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T06:32:09.632000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-09T06:32:25.073000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1249250159704014879", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "思路是一樣，但為了適應環境已要變得很多", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T06:34:08.019000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1249250917996429424", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "艾爾瓦很強，但是被主流麻毒控死，除非對面手牌事故。所以經歷完一堆選角測牌後，選了可愛的阿帕，因為她的纏繞很合現在這個吃命鑰的meta，拖對面時間一流。", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T06:37:08.810000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1249251516066435155", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為艾爾不在了，命鑰的出血位要補上新的，我改成血肉狂宴，因為這隊的思路是全隊秒，不再單殺，所以不用夜色。而且，狂宴可以猜對面手牌，能更好地控住", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T06:39:31.401000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1249252291362553878", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "最後是雷亞換神父，同是隨機高額爆發，我選擇血厚一點的，攻擊力差點也可以，因為現環境的T1單殺能力還是很強，雷亞太易死了。\n而且，這樣打，也不會有回血牌，所有牌都是攻擊，對於一隊誰死先都沒所謂，沒有所謂保核的隊來說更好", "timestamp": "2024-06-09T06:42:36.246000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
